<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạṭmny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạṭmny byki ạlmsyḥ byʿtny
 mrfwʿẗ rạsk mạtkẖạfysẖ wʿmrhạ mạ htnḥny
 ạṭmny dạ mạfysẖ klạm hyhmny
 yạ knysty qwmy mạtqlqysẖ wlạ ạ̉y ḥạjẗ thzny
 ạlqrạr- yạ knysẗ lyki ạ̹lh ʿẓym sẖạylk fy
 ʿynh wḥạmyki
 wkl ạ̉bwạb ạljḥym mstḥyl tqwy̱ ʿlyki
 2- ạtklmy llsẖʿb qwly wʿlmy
 wqt ạlmḥn mạtdmʿysẖ bạlʿks gẖny wrnmy
 ạtklmy ḥḍn ạlmsyḥ fyh ạḥtmy
 byh ạfrḥy wmạtzʿlysẖ fy ʿz mạ bttạ̉lmy</lyrics>
<author>mynạ mjdy, mạjd mwsy̱</author>
<hymn_number>9611</hymn_number>
</song>